[The report includes a France24 video, between Paris and Conakry; see the source URL. This report is very comprehensive, covering all the challenges faced in combatting EVD. Although a lot of what is written here has been stated in the past, it is important to review what the lessons from the past outbreaks are and try to implement changes accordingly. - Mod.LK]

